Parliament, Wednesday, 29 July 2020 – The Chairperson of the Standing Committee on Public Accounts, Mr Mkhuleko Hlengwa, will tomorrow participate in a panel discussion on corruption.
	
	Details are as follows:
	Date: Thursday, 30 July 2020
	Time: 10:00
